Before I knew it, it was May, The season when young leaves are the most beautiful
This kind of season makes me totally impressed!
Tsu I bought it at last! A shiny rice cooker for one person!
The money I got from pachinko was great!
I would call it a test run
That guy often can do that alone
Even when I was at home, I had to leave everything to my mother
It\u2019s true that if you have a hardworking mother, your daughter won\u2019t be able to do anything
I'm so impressed with the rice cooker
If you buy a refrigerator or a TV, you might be crazy

I've become a constitution that I can't get out of ramen anymore
However, a good part-time job is not easy, I'm gonna play pachinko again, However, I feel that such a fluke will never live again
Oh, Asami-san, Letter from parents' home?
